{
  "name": "Homework OCR",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "seconds",
              "seconds": 30
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "schedule",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "functionCode": "// This is a placeholder - replace with actual Telegram or Webhook trigger\n// For now, this outputs sample data for testing\n\nconst sampleData = [\n  {\n    json: {\n      file_id: \"sample_image.jpg\",\n      caption: \"Homework test\"\n    }\n  }\n];\n\nreturn sampleData;"
      },
      "id": "manual-trigger",
      "name": "Manual Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.function",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gemini-2.0-flash",
        "messages": {
          "messages": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "你是一個功課辨識助手。\n\n任務：辨識圖片中的功課內容。\n\n輸出要求：\n1. 只輸出JSON陣列，無其他文字\n2. 忽略：日期標題、值日生、學校通告\n3. 科目：數學、中文、英文、科學、地理、歷史、公經社、電腦、音樂、視藝、體育\n4. Detail：完整功課描述\n5. Deadline：格式 DD/MM（如 21/3）\n\n輸出格式：\n[{\"subject\": \"科目\", \"detail\": \"內容\", \"deadline\": \"DD/MM\"}]\n\n如果圖片中沒有功課，輸出：[]"
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": \"image_url",
                  "image_url": {
                    "url": "={{ $json.imageUrl }}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "ai-gemini",
      "name": "AI - Gemini OCR",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chatOpenAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [450, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "append",
        "sheetId": "YOUR_SHEET_ID",
        "range": "Sheet1!A:D",
        "options": {
          "valueInputMode": "USER_ENTERED"
        },
        "values": {
          "values": [
            [
              "={{ $now.format(\"YYYY-MM-DD\") }}",
              "={{ $json.subject }}",
              "={{ $json.detail }}",
              "={{ $json.deadline }}"
            ]
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "google-sheets",
      "name": "Google Sheets",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
      "typeVersion": 3.5,
      "position": [650, 300]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Manual Trigger": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "AI - Gemini OCR",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "AI - Gemini OCR": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Google Sheets",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  },
